      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>Wait, before you finalize anything, I need to be clear: if you're rushing this because you're genuinely facing a production shutdown or an immediate shortage, I might be able to talk my manager into a bulk-order discount for a longer-term contract. But if this is just a standard restock, I can't justify the \"urgent\" pricing tier. Are you actually in an emergency situation with your current supply?",
